title: Bobby's Dangerous Kayaking Experience + Amy’s Morning Corny After Dark (Uncensored) + Lunchbox Heckled By His Neighbors
itunes:title: Bobby's Dangerous Kayaking Experience + Amy’s Morning Corny After Dark (Uncensored) + Lunchbox Heckled By His Neighbors
description:
Bobby talks about his weekend in Boise, Idaho learning to kayak for an upcoming episode of his NatGeo TV show “Breaking Bobby Bones”. Check out Amy’s uncensored version of “The Morning Corny After Dark”. Lunchbox got yelled at by his neighbors. Amy got to spend time with her dad at her house for the first time in a long time. Plus, Brantley Gilbert stops by the studio to talk about his huge man cave, the songs he wrote for Jason Aldean, and fans getting his name tattooed on them!
